			<h4><a id="comment_link_64429908" name="comment_link_64429908" href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23304482&amp;cid=64429908" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64429908)" >The FAA will have blood on its hands</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64429908" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64429908); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Interesting)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~NewtonsLaw">NewtonsLaw</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~NewtonsLaw">( 409638 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64429908">		
